io.spine.query

Class EntityCriterion<S extends EntityState<?>,V,B extends EntityQueryBuilder<?,S,B,?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.query.EntityCriterion<S,V,B>
  • Type Parameters:
    S - the type of entity state
    V - the type of the column values for this criterion
    B - the type of the builder in scope of which this criterion exists

    public final class EntityCriterion<S extends EntityState<?>,V,B extends EntityQueryBuilder<?,S,B,?>>
extends java.lang.Object
    An expression which sets the value to compare for the EntityColumn in scope of a EntityQueryBuilder when building an EntityQuery.
